subscriptionurl.label: Subscription URL:
tokenurl.label: Token:
subscription.validationType.checkbox: Disable validation (should be used with care for well curated collections or sources)
nosubscriptionmessage.info: You are not subscribed to Open Concept Lab. Please go to the configuration page to setup the subscription.
avoidUpdatesInfo.text: Avoid importing during data entry hours, because the operation may significantly slow down the system.
unsubscribeinfo.text: If you unsubscribe, no concepts will be deleted nor changed. All information about subscription will be deleted from your system
fixAllErrorsMessage.text: Please fix all errors so that you can continue to get updates. It may require fixing concepts locally (e.g. creating concept classes, changing concept names to eliminate duplicates, etc.) or asking your dictionary manager for fixes in the OCL.
fixAllErrorsWarning.text: All items from the last failing update will be imported again. Make sure all errors have been fixed locally or on the OpenConceptLab server.
ignoreAllErrorsQuestion.text: Your last import ended with errors. Do you want to run that import again or ignore all errors?
